      "name": "CPB hemolysis applicability constraint",
      "description": "Model applicability is constrained to centrifugal blood pumps operating within the FDA generic pump geometry envelope, blood viscosity 0.0035–0.0040 Pa·s, hematocrit 35–45%, and rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM. Extrapolation beyond these bounds is not supported by the validation evidence base."
    },
